import { View, Text } from "react-native";
import { Link } from "react-router-native";
import { menuStyle } from "../styles/components";
import { CalendarIcon, GraphIcon, HomeIcon } from "./icons";

const Menu = () =>
    <View style={menuStyle.menu}>
        <Text style={menuStyle.title}>Workouts</Text>
        <View style={menuStyle.sectionContainer}>
            <View style={[menuStyle.section, menuStyle.sectionActive]}>
                <Link to="/">
                    <HomeIcon/>
                </Link>
            </View>
            <View style={menuStyle.section}>
                <Link to="/calendar">
                    <CalendarIcon/>
                </Link>
            </View>
            <View style={menuStyle.section}>
                <Link to="/statistics">
                    <GraphIcon/>
                </Link>
            </View>
        </View>
    </View>

export default Menu;
